<topic id='business_definition_care_home_with_nursing.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>NHS Business Definition: Care Home With Nursing - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>

  <p>
A 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_care_home_with_nursing">Care Home With Nursing</xref>
 is an 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation_site">ORGANISATION SITE</xref>
  </p>
  <p>
A 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_care_home_with_nursing">Care Home With Nursing</xref>
 is a 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_care_home">Care Home</xref>
 where, in addition to personal care and accommodation, is a place where qualified nursing care is provided, to ensure that the full needs of the 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_person">PERSON</xref>
 are met.  </p>
  <p>
Examples of 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_care_home_with_nursing">Care Homes With Nursing</xref>
 include:  </p>
  <ul>
      <li>
         <div>
            <p>Nursing home</p>
         </div>
      </li>
      <li>
         <div>
            <p>Convalescent home with nursing</p>
         </div>
      </li>
      <li>
         <div>
            <p>Respite care with nursing</p>
         </div>
      </li>
      <li>
         <div>
            <p>Mental health crisis house with nursing.</p>
         </div>
      </li>
  </ul>
  <p>
Note: the 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_care_quality_commission">Care Quality Commission</xref>
 definition of nursing care is:  </p>
  <p>
"Nursing care means any 
      <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_service">SERVICE</xref>
 provided by a 
      <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_nurse">NURSE</xref>
 and involves:  </p>
  <ul>
      <li>
         <div>
            <p>The provision of care, or</p>
         </div>
      </li>
      <li>
         <div>
            <p>
The planning, supervision or delegation of the provision of care, other than any 
                  <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_service">SERVICES</xref>
 which, by their nature and the circumstances in which they are provided, do not need to be provided by a 
                  <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_nurse">NURSE</xref>
."        </p>
         </div>
      </li>
  </ul>
  <p>
For further information on 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_care_home">Care Homes</xref>
, see the 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_care_quality_commission">Care Quality Commission</xref>
 website at: 
    <xref href="https://www.cqc.org.uk/what-we-do/services-we-regulate/care-homes"
            scope="external"
            format="html">Care homes</xref>
.  </p>

